{{ 'section-thank-you-newsletter.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="page-thank-you">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="thank-you-content">
      <span class="thank-you-icon">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="60"
          height="60"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="feather feather-inbox"
        >
          <polyline points="22 12 16 12 14 15 10 15 8 12 2 12"></polyline><path d="M5.45 5.11L2 12v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6l-3.45-6.89A2 2 0 0 0 16.76 4H7.24a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11z"></path>
        </svg>
      </span>

      <h1>Welcome to the Edge.</h1>
      <h2>You’re now subscribed to the most specialized newsletter for Shopify Plus merchants.</h2>

      <div class="rte">
        <p>
          Your subscription is confirmed. Every week, you’ll receive a single, high-signal email with actionable tactics
          on the two most critical growth levers for 2025: B2B expansion and strategic AI integration.
        </p>

        <div class="action-callout">
          <strong>Don't miss an issue:</strong> Please add [Your Email Address] to your trusted contacts.
        </div>

        <h3>My Philosophy</h3>
        <p>
          I don’t share generic industry news. I deliver focused, field-tested insights from my work in the Shopify
          trenches—the kind of strategies that help you automate operations, professionalize your wholesale channel, and
          drive real revenue.
        </p>

        <h3>While You Wait for the Next Issue...</h3>
        <p>Explore the archive and get a head start with these popular articles:</p>

        <ul class="thank-you-links styled-links">
          <li><a href="/#insights">Why Your ERP Integration is Failing Your B2B Launch</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#insights">3 AI Tools for Precision Wholesale Demand Forecasting in 2025</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#insights">The End of Manual Order Entry: Automating B2B on Shopify Plus</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Ready for Implementation?</h3>
        <p>
          When you're ready to move from insights to implementation, my <strong>B2B & AI Opportunity Roadmap</strong> is
          the definitive first step.
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top: 3rem; text-align: center;">
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-brand btn-brand-primary">Book the $1,950 Roadmap</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="thank-you-closing">
        <p>— Robert Foster</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

